ATTRIBUTION NOTICE

OP_NEXUS is built on OP_NET — the smart contract execution layer for Bitcoin
Layer 1. The authors acknowledge and thank the OP_NET and btc-vision teams for
making programmable finance on Bitcoin possible.

  OP_NET Runtime:   https://opnet.org
  btc-vision:       https://github.com/btc-vision
  btc-runtime:      https://github.com/btc-vision/btc-runtime  (MIT)
  native-swap:      https://github.com/btc-vision/native-swap  (MIT)

