DEPLOYED CONTRACT

The following contract deployment on Bitcoin Layer 1 is the canonical
reference implementation of OP_NEXUS v1.0:

  Network:  OP_NET Testnet
  Address:  opt1sqpup5mjysflvxucr2qhpg6td7hdsyu8z05sngpw3
  Binary:   OPNexus.wasm (SHA-256 to be published post-audit)

This deployment is immutable. No admin keys exist. No upgrade mechanism exists.
The treasury fee recipient address embedded in this deployment is controlled
by the original author and represents the author's economic stake in the
protocol as described in the project documentation.

Any fork or redeployment of this Software must comply with the MIT License
above and is encouraged to clearly distinguish itself from the canonical
deployment to avoid user confusion.

