DISCLAIMER

OP_NEXUS is experimental software deployed on a nascent blockchain execution
environment. It has not been formally audited at the time of initial deployment.
Users interact with it at their own risk.

The authors make no representations or warranties about the suitability of
this software for any purpose, including but not limited to financial
transactions. Nothing in this software constitutes financial advice.

Smart contracts are immutable once deployed. Bugs, if present, cannot be
patched post-deployment. Users are encouraged to review the source code,
the SECURITY.md analysis, and the WHITEPAPER.md before committing capital.
